Instruction: Use the papertowel to wipe the kitchencabinet, and then throw the used papertowel into the garbagecan.
Turn on the lightswitch, and then use the rag to clean the wallpictureframe, towelrack, and bookshelf.
Take the rag to the sink to clean it, and then use it to wipe the desk.
Take the apple to the faucet, wash it clean, cut them into slices, put them on the plate, and place the plate on the coffeetable.
Use the duster to remove dust from the rug, unplug the toaster, and clean it with the rag.
Use a brush to clean the remote control, picture frame, and clock, then wipe down the TV stand with a cloth
Cut the chicken and the carrot into pieces, place them on the oventray, season with the condimentbottle.
Wash the apples and plums, slice the apples with the kitchenknife, and place the apples neatly on the cutting board.
Put the clothespile in the sink to wash it, and then use the rag to clean the sink.
